    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i'm a wellness coach for a big tech firm and i'm putting together some slides for our leadership team. can u give me some tips on grooming and overall appearance that help employees look more authoritative and professional when they're in high-stakes boardroom meetings? like what are the key things they should focus on to make sure they're taken seriously?",
