      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "For a boardroom, a sharp, conservative look is key to projecting authority. Men should opt for well-tailored suits in dark, solid colors, paired with crisp shirts and ties that match the corporate tone. Women should favor tailored suiting or professional dresses that are impeccably fitted, ensuring the overall presentation is polished and understated. The focus should be on impeccable grooming—neat hair, clean nails, and minimal, high-quality accessories—to convey competence and seriousness.",
