      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. can u go into more detail about the hair part? like, if someone has more natural or textured hair, or maybe wears specific cultural styles, what would u suggest to keep it looking \"polished\" and \"professional\" for these meetings? i want to make sure the advice is practical for everyone.",
